  1AC:  Call  PlayerFaceNpc ( .Npc:Partner 00000005 )
  1C0:  Call  SpeakToPlayer ( .Npc:Player 000D0004 000A0001 00000005 00140160 ) % ...Tee hee hee... I hope you're right, Twink. Than ...
